game/Assets/AssetStoreTools*

# Asset Store packs are licensed to the Unity ACCOUNT that bought them and may not be
# redistributed — and this repo is PUBLIC, so committing them would be exactly that.
# They are drop-ins: import the pack and re-bootstrap (scripts/import-assetstore.ps1) and
# the world picks it up; with no pack the bootstrap falls back to the CC0 Kenney kits.
# See docs/asset-store-import.md.
game/Assets/RPGPP_LT/
game/Assets/RPGPP_LT.meta
game/Assets/SimpleNaturePack/
game/Assets/SimpleNaturePack.meta
game/Assets/LowPolyDungeonsLite/
game/Assets/LowPolyDungeonsLite.meta
game/Assets/Handpainted_Grass_and_Ground_Textures/
game/Assets/Handpainted_Grass_and_Ground_Textures.meta

# Locally extracted Asset Store audio. The public repo keeps code/fallbacks only; licensed
# source clips stay on the purchaser's machine and are packed into their local player build.
game/Assets/Resources/Music/*.wav
game/Assets/Resources/Music/*.wav.meta
game/Assets/Resources/Music/*.mp3
game/Assets/Resources/Music/*.mp3.meta
game/Assets/Resources/Music/*.ogg
game/Assets/Resources/Music/*.ogg.meta
game/Assets/Resources/Sfx/
game/Assets/Resources/Sfx.meta

